{"tid":2254902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爭議事件一定係連登仔嘅錯 不服來辯","createTime":"2020-10-23T07:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T07:31:28.000Z","uid":23468,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7446e520705020a7379b9d80a213b32e9cdae47f","tid":2254902,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"永遠正經討論總有一群聲音<br />\n<br />\n就好似光時事件：<br />\n<br />\n初衷根本就唔係開舖頭賺錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBiNqM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBiNqM6.jpg&h=eed5d42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起壇嗰陣就日日上嚟開post<br />\n用極高調手法宣傳收益全數用作支援手足<br />\n好老實如果唔係用依句宣傳一早摺咗<br />\n<br />\n無耐之後又話告急又話頂唔住又開post<br />\n結果連登仔再一次即刻狗衝去買嘢<br />\n貴2成都照買 原因又係咩呢？<br />\n原來我買貴市價2成嘅嘢係幫高層供樓？<br />\n<br />\n有違初衷嘅事點解唔可以討論？<br />\n連登仔作為長期恩客<br />\n直情可以話係冇股權嘅股東<br />\n開個post想理性討論有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n事實證據已經擺在眼前<br />\n但係盲撐嘅表示睇唔到 唔知道<br />\n然而一直不斷攻擊連登係兒登<br />\n垃圾集中營，五毛討論區<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇光時回應post下邊嘅留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUtUQaU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUtUQaU.png&h=cde2f651&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35BvovU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35BvovU.png&h=919e2a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4chKsXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4chKsXA.png&h=c3945a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n一直話兒登多分化多五毛<br />\n一直叫人唔好睇兒登<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你哋係咩居心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到底邊個喺度搞緊分化呢？周圍屈毛呢？<br />\n到底邊個喺度帶緊風向叫人唔好睇連登呢？<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aed16c258a6ba2e8e3d343e7215256091ef88d9","tid":2254902,"uid":158645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"連登呢個地方都痴撚線 充斥社會垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252297</a>"},{"pid":"74629c012ec1337894a75f27ac936ee95b13e095","tid":2254902,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aed16c258a6ba2e8e3d343e7215256091ef88d9","tid":2254902,"uid":158645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"連登呢個地方都痴撚線 充斥社會垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252297</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"由渣哥事件開始<br />\n已經不斷有聲音叫大家唔洗理連登<br />\n但係每一件事都係證據確鑿<br />\n<br />\n到底連登仔錯咗啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99b781c8e088058e58fa681561e575c417d1c57","tid":2254902,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"去課自己信果個囉<br />\n<br />\n嘈來晒氣<br />\n<br />\n又唔係一定要課<br />\n<br />\nd黃絲課完柒左講到課得唔抵咁<br />\n<br />\n唔課蕭生就預左有假嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係Call g咁 乾乾淨淨大波唔要<br />\n<br />\n要件不明來歷 到中左性病又起到嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e607c2a741141decdb8abf4b43bfe587352d72f","tid":2254902,"uid":158645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74629c012ec1337894a75f27ac936ee95b13e095","tid":2254902,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aed16c258a6ba2e8e3d343e7215256091ef88d9","tid":2254902,"uid":158645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"連登呢個地方都痴撚線 充斥社會垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252297</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"由渣哥事件開始<br />\n已經不斷有聲音叫大家唔洗理連登<br />\n但係每一件事都係證據確鑿<br />\n<br />\n到底連登仔錯咗啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"個post過萬正評<br 